description:
Gogobot is your go to place for places to go. With over 725,000 reviews and 4M photos, Gogobot provides you with personalized recommendations on where to Eat, Play or Stay wherever you are.

* Go Local: Explore the best of what's near you, wherever you are!

* GoGo This Week: Now live in SF, NYC, LA, London, San Diego and Silicon Valley; every week Gogobot recommends fun, unique things to do in your city based on your interests. Don't worry, we're working hard to cover more cities soon, stay tuned!

* Go Adventure: Whether your cliff diving, lounging or dive bar-ing, get the best recommendations for you.

* Go Tribal: Luxury, Budget, Foodies and more come together in Tribes to help you find the stuff you'll like best based on your personality and interests.

* Go Together: Connect with friends to make the most of your free time, collaboratively planning nights on the town to exotic vacations

* Go Share: Give your friends & followers serious FOMO by creating postcards of your adventures.

TOP APP

* Featured as “Best New App by Apple” 
* Named “New & Noteworthy” in more than 20 countries
* Named in the “Best of” Apple App collection as best news application, along with Yelp, Airbnb, [...] and more...
* Featured in USA Today, Business Insider, Mashable, TechCrunch, BGR, PC Mag, and more...

releaseNotes:
- Get there faster: See a GogoThisWeek you just can't wait to get the skinny on? Tapping on it from your home screen will now take you directly to that recommendation! Woohoo!

- Fixed an issue causing some users to have to choose their destination every time they open the app.

- Other stability improvements and performance enhancements!
